    <keyword>ECHO</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC specifies a standard for the ARPA Internet community.  Hosts on the ARPA Internet that choose to implement a Echo Protocol are expected to adopt and implement this standard.  The Echo service simply sends back to the originating source any data it receives.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
